{"tid":1023553,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(少圖)半live岡山鳥取米子之旅","createTime":"2019-02-16T00:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T14:44:50.000Z","uid":236627,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a96d99c1dbefd3b26925448abd639925cbb4fc","tid":1023553,"uid":236627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T00:45:07.000Z","msg":"單身狗在經過214的重傷後，215當然是飛去日本散心。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jz0fLZu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJz0fLZu.jpg&h=6d995a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jtnqoMe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjtnqoMe.jpg&h=18ecd02f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n10點幾 入到機場，再在垃圾環亞食早餐，就夠鐘上機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZCqoM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZCqoM6.jpg&h=5c2820f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早廿分鐘到又點，個天同我心情一尻樣咁灰呀。 搭車出岡山駅仲要塞足大半個鐘車。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNvzg81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNvzg81.jpg&h=22e4c8c4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Szmnq2r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzmnq2r.jpg&h=cd1900fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NrZ0W9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrZ0W9a.jpg&h=3e096d8a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O19TxHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO19TxHA.jpg&h=bc78c746&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3HNB9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3HNB9g.jpg&h=97d12f2c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wn0vzVZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWn0vzVZ.jpg&h=c5166f7c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n6點呀，屌，4點多少少落機，6點先出到岡山，我仲要無食個垃圾飛機餐，好彩想食果間燒肉近個駅，唔係真係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7jL8hw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7jL8hw.jpg&h=3651fb3d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PHp0XaW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPHp0XaW.jpg&h=27235eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 順道放埋間房個view，望住個車站好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bb358fac55992cfdada37acc87bfc25bc8f81e","tid":1023553,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"住via inn?"},{"pid":"9b00b65cd4e727f5d8d1c00f99e89528f1b14fe2","tid":1023553,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2bb358fac55992cfdada37acc87bfc25bc8f81e","tid":1023553,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"住via inn?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:54:57.000Z","msg":"呢間via位置真係一流 仲有輕早食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係間房細d 但裝修都ok"},{"pid":"cd5de684dc0599d5ee4ffc9601f9dd633b59d144","tid":1023553,"uid":236627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b00b65cd4e727f5d8d1c00f99e89528f1b14fe2","tid":1023553,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2bb358fac55992cfdada37acc87bfc25bc8f81e","tid":1023553,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"住via inn?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T02:54:57.000Z","msg":"呢間via位置真係一流 仲有輕早食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係間房細d 但裝修都ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T03:01:08.000Z","msg":"早餐d酥好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bf1d72472adebff6d1884e7875f2ebbe6e7e30","tid":1