g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaS36TY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaS36TY.jpg&h=22664db8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ibAYbkE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FibAYbkE.jpg&h=dbf6b427&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mrak87m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrak87m.jpg&h=c3cd111b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w5zx0d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw5zx0d4.jpg&h=222d2655&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n入到去仲暖過係出邊, 仲要行到我衫都除埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ctd64KJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtd64KJ.jpg&h=7c22c775&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n下邊果句, 大家可以慢慢幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CeZmTC6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCeZmTC6.jpg&h=22f425e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NP8VX4P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNP8VX4P.jpg&h=d800d2e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uyXjFib.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuyXjFib.jpg&h=7fb51a0c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n雖然我今日未去睇真的瀨戶海, 係到睇住個假的先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSUYVRx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSUYVRx.jpg&h=c363ccf3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UM4mTDe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUM4mTDe.jpg&h=2b52ec5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KH14RpN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKH14RpN.jpg&h=dadb3d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇唔出有咩黃金的黃金殿堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KGMkh4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KGMkh4.jpg&h=d35e91e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GV6DVRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGV6DVRB.jpg&h=c636a2a3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nE2枝野似咩, 大家可以慢慢幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zToZFnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzToZFnL.jpg&h=1d350c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JToF9f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJToF9f7.jpg&h=5fafef38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7827ee9393b5aad5ee0fa27d08e9b79c7acc524a","tid":1023553,"uid":236627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46b6e1cbdc0c0f0d75aec306e8ec4f570aae4230","tid":1023553,"uid":95881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e2c3fe8ed6f590ce166db252133629b21decc05","tid":1023553,"uid":230818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:13:40.000Z","msg":"去岡山 鳥取 米子 <br />\n<br />\n係咪好似得岡山有一班直航?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"米子有直航<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"岡山入, 米子走咪得, 最後果日仲可以買返隻蟹返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b5b70790bf490e0da7327011c491ddb88a611b","tid":1023553,"uid":236627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:27:45.000Z","msg":"一出門見, 竟然見到呢塊牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOv5A0W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOv5A0W.jpg&h=e7a74f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實佢話半個鐘, 慢慢行可以行到1個鐘囉, 差D比佢呃左搞到MISS巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ppaNdR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ppaNdR.jpg&h=02befd24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hAAtyTT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhAAtyTT.jpg&h=9b92f413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n少人同無車到我企係到360影完都無問題的鐵路, 半個鐘先有一班車系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puyrkyX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuyrkyX.jpg&h=f463fa27&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之後緊係上BUS去埋附近的滿奇洞, 但係E邊真係算尻數, 半個鐘行完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6Xzuv2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6Xzuv2.jpg&h=5c5f16ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4M09uB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4M09uB.jpg&h=2352cd5c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCeeuuy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCeeuuy.jpg&h=2d7c80d0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43bXsga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43bXsga.jpg&h=625e42b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uM4mTWb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuM4mTWb.jpg&h=79bee32a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjbP2PC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjbP2PC.jpg&h=13e3a35d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nBUaNgj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBUaNgj.jpg&h=03f14978&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uk5JnPG.jpg\" data-thu